ns0:listitem.ns0:para:
seamless integration of profiling (conditional
documents) with external bibliographies and
glossaries;

ns0:section.ns0:para:
The Perl script db4-entities.pl, also included
in the DocBook V5.0 distribution attempts to perform this replacement
for you. To use the script, perform the following steps:

ns0:example.ns0:programlisting:
namespace db = "http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"

include "docbook.rnc" inherit = db {
  # redefine important element as notAllowed
  db.important = notAllowed
}

namespace db = "http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"

include "docbook.rnc" inherit = db {
  db.common.linking.attributes = empty
}

ns0:step.ns0:programlisting:
namespace html = "http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
namespace mml = "http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"
namespace db = "http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"

include "/path/to/docbook.rnc" {
  db._any.mml = external "mathml/mathml2.rnc"
  db._any =
    element * - (db:* | html:* | mml:*) {
      (attribute * { text }
       | text
       | db._any)*
    }
}

namespace html = "http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
namespace db = "http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
namespace svg = "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"

include "/path/to/docbook.rnc" {
  db._any.svg = external "svg/svg11.rnc"
  db._any =
    element * - (db:* | html:* | svg:*) {
      (attribute * { text }
       | text
       | db._any)*
    }
}

ns0:answer.ns0:programlisting:
namespace html = "http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
namespace mml = "http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"
namespace db = "http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
namespace svg = "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"

include "/path/to/docbook.rnc" {
  db._any.mml = external "mahtml/mathml2.rnc"
  db._any.svg = external "svg/svg11.rnc"
  db._any =
    element * - (db:* | html:* | mml:* | svg:*) {
      (attribute * { text }
       | text
       | db._any)*
    }
}
